---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Attire">

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Dress Code</span>
      <h1>What to Wear</h1>
      <div class="divider">
        <div class="divider-line"></div>
        <div class="divider-diamond"></div>
        <div class="divider-line"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="header-sub">We'd love for our guests to feel as beautiful as the setting.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="attire-grid">

        <!-- DRESS CODE CARD -->
        <div class="attire-card">
          <span class="section-label">The Dress Code</span>
          <h2>Garden Formal</h2>
          <div class="divider">
            <div class="divider-line"></div>
            <div class="divider-diamond"></div>
            <div class="divider-line"></div>
          </div>
          <p>Think refined garden party — elegant but not stiff. We invite you to embrace the beauty of the estate with thoughtful, polished attire that complements the natural surroundings.</p>
          <ul class="attire-list">
            <li>Suits, blazers, or dress trousers for gentlemen</li>
            <li>Midi or maxi dresses, elegant separates, or dressy jumpsuits for ladies</li>
            <li>Florals and soft patterns are warmly encouraged</li>
            <li>Please avoid white, ivory, or black</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- PALETTE CARD -->
        <div class="attire-card palette-card">
          <span class="section-label">Dress Code — Garden Formal</span>
          <div class="palette-circles">
            <div class="palette-item">
              <div class="palette-circle" style="background:#BED2BC; border-color:#BED2BC;"></div>
              <span class="palette-name">Sage</span>
            </div>
            <div class="palette-item">
              <div class="palette-circle" style="background:#EAECC5; border-color:#C8BE8C;"></div>
              <span class="palette-name">Cream</span>
            </div>
            <div class="palette-item">
              <div class="palette-circle" style="background:#C8BE8C; border-color:#C8BE8C;"></div>
              <span class="palette-name">Sand</span>
            </div>
            <div class="palette-item">
              <div class="palette-circle" style="background:#C08480; border-color:#C08480;"></div>
              <span class="palette-name">Blush</span>
            </div>
            <div class="palette-item">
              <div class="palette-circle" style="background:#B4924C; border-color:#B4924C;"></div>
              <span class="palette-name">Gold</span>
            </div>
            <div class="palette-item">
              <div class="palette-circle" style="background:#494E3C; border-color:#494E3C;"></div>
              <span class="palette-name">Forest</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="palette-note">We invite you to lean into soft, earthy tones that complement the estate gardens. Florals and patterns are warmly welcome. Please avoid white, ivory, and black.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- ADDITIONAL NOTES -->
      <div class="attire-notes">
        <div class="attire-note-item">
          <span class="section-label">Footwear</span>
          <p>The ceremony and cocktail hour take place on grass and garden paths. We recommend block heels, wedges, or flats for comfort.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="attire-note-divider"></div>
        <div class="attire-note-item">
          <span class="section-label">Weather</span>
          <p>June evenings in Hudson Valley can be cool. We suggest bringing a light wrap or jacket for the later hours of the evening.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="attire-note-divider"></div>
        <div class="attire-note-item">
          <span class="section-label">Questions?</span>
          <p>If you have any questions about attire, please don't hesitate to reach out directly and we'll be happy to help.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .header-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--swan-brown);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0.8rem auto 0;
  }

  .attire-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .attire-card {
    background: var(--swan-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--swan-sand);
    padding: 2.5rem;
  }
  .attire-card h2 { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .attire-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .attire-list li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--swan-brown);
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--swan-sand);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .attire-list li::before {
    content: '✦';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-size: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--swan-blush);
    top: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* ── Palette Card ── */
  .palette-card {
    background: var(--swan-cream);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .palette-circles {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .palette-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .palette-circle {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .palette-name {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--swan-brown);
  }

  .palette-note {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--swan-brown);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 340px;
    margin: 0 !important;
  }

  /* ── Additional Notes ── */
  .attire-notes {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0;
    background: var(--swan-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--swan-sand);
    padding: 2.5rem;
  }

  .attire-note-item {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  .attire-note-item:first-child { padding-left: 0; }
  .attire-note-item:last-child { padding-right: 0; }
  .attire-note-item p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--swan-brown);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .attire-note-divider {
    width: 1px;
    background: var(--swan-sand);
    align-self: stretch;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .attire-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .attire-notes { flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; }
    .attire-note-item { padding: 0 !important; }
    .attire-note-divider { width: 100%; height: 1px; }
  }
</style>